commitResults.messageTitle: Implement ModBookTime class and change Timeslot to use ModBookTime
commitResults.messageBody:
ModBookTime created to encapsulate LocalTimes - so that we can
change the formatter as well as write a method to parse different
formats of time strings in the future.

The `jackson-datatpe-jdk8` module seems to serialize `Path`s to
their absolute path rather than relative path, and this causes
it to fail tests
